---
title: Cheesy Curried Beans and Mash with Cucumber and Baby Leaf Salad
description: Flip a classic jacket potato on its head by making a mash of it, then pile it up with curried beans before finishing with cheese. A fresh salad on the side adds extra veg to this wholesome vegetarian meal.
